        "text": "This issue essentially has to be solved in apache-fineract ( back-end) however, It would be great if you could deal with the community-app side issue. So, try to make the value field mandatory, and try to make the necessary front-end validation in the `add collateral via more button` please ignore the new loan account method since we might need to solve that in the back-end.", 
