            "program_year": 2017, 
            "id": 5082325438169088
        }, 
        "text": "Hi, Matthew the issue does exist, When creating a loan application, try adding the collateral initially with a value. Then once it's added,  you can remove the value and submit. It still submits without an error.  Also, try to submit collateral using the more drop-down button in the loan account view, you will notice that the value and description are not mandatory. Please see the attached gif.", 
